With Lazar Markovic suspended, He is expected to figure in tonight's Europa League game against Besiktas, with Brendan Rodgers having full confidence in how Ibe is developing.

Liverpool are in the process of reviewing a clutch of contractual situations. Philippe Coutinho and Daniel Sturridge recently signed long-term extensions, while talks are ongoing with Raheem Sterling and Jordan Henderson.

They are all players who Liverpool want to build their future around and Ibe falls into the same category.

